      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation that must be seen to be fully appreciated. This vehicle remains in showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment throughout its life. The exterior features a flawless, mirror-like paint finish with absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, complemented by pristine alloy wheels and factory-spec tires with deep tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, devoid of any creasing or wear, and the interior still carries that distinct factory-fresh scent. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified specialists. This car drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in its absolute prime.",
